election_record.label: Connecticut 1823 State Senate

overview.note: John T. Peters received 37 votes as John S. Peters.
Abel Wheeler received 12 votes as Abiel Wheeler.
Elias Perkins received 9 votes as Elisha Perkins and 9 votes as Enock Perkins.
Samuel A. Foot received 3 votes as Samuel Foot.
William W. Ellsworth received 2 votes as William Ellsworth.
Epaphroditus Champion received 1 vote as Epaphroditus Champion, Jr and 5 votes as Epaphroditus Chapman.
Solomon Taintor received 1 vote as S. Taintor.
Austin Olcott received 16 votes as Augustin Olcott and 1 vote as Augustus Olcott.
Elisha Phelps received 1 vote as Elisha Phillips.
Thomas S. Williams received 1 vote as Thomas Williams.

sub_unit.note: Elisha Phelps received 22 votes as Elias Phelps.

sub_unit.note: The votes from Brookfield were rejected.
